comments: Ellis (SAC) cleanly deflects the ball away from Banchero (ORL).
Fox (SAC) avoids making contact with Banchero's (ORL) arm as he contests the shot near the rim.
Banchero (ORL) and Barnes (SAC) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
After the initial contact, Anthony (ORL) moves slightly forward towards Ellis (SAC) and marginal contact occurs during the defensive switch.
Banchero (ORL) brings his arm forward towards Ellis' (SAC) legal forearm, and the contact during the back down is marginal.
Sabonis (SAC) does not extend his left arm into Wagner (ORL) as they come together in pursuit of the rebound.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Replay review of the out of bounds called on Suggs (ORL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful.  Fox (SAC) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds, and possession is correctly awarded to the Magic.
Fox (SAC) absorbs the marginal contact from Wagner (ORL) that occurs as he jumps to contest the driving shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) is moving alongside Banchero's (ORL) path, and marginal contact occurs as they come together at the same spot during the drive.
Sabonis (SAC) contests Banchero's (ORL) pass attempt, and the contact is marginal.
Sabonis (SAC) jumps from point A to point B and initiates contact with Anthony's (ORL) lower body as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Suggs (ORL) extends his hand into Fox's (SAC) torso and delivers contact that affects his SQBR.  This contact occurs prior to, and causes, Fox to then step on the halfcourt line.
Isaac (ORL) establishes himself in Sabonis' (SAC) path and absorbs the contact during the screen.
Barnes (SAC) and Isaac (ORL) briefly engage and disengage as they pursue the rebound.
Barnes (SAC) raises his forearm to brace for the imminent contact from Anthony (ORL), and the contact during the shot attempt is marginal.
Sabonis (SAC) and Isaac (ORL) pursue the rebound, and the contact is marginal.
Suggs (ORL) delivers contact to Ellis (SAC) in the air and affects his return to the floor.
Suggs (ORL) stumbles into Ellis (SAC) during the in-bounds play and the contact is marginal.
Fox (SAC) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Banchero's (ORL) arm.
